        <section class="about-section">
          <h1>About Blockchain Web Services</h1>
          <p>Blockchain Web Services (BWS) is a comprehensive platform that simplifies blockchain integration for developers and businesses worldwide. We believe that blockchain technology should be accessible to everyone, not just Web3 experts.</p>
          
          <h2>Our Mission</h2>
          <p>We are dedicated to democratizing blockchain technology by providing easy-to-use APIs and solutions that enable mass-market adoption. Our platform bridges the gap between complex blockchain infrastructure and practical business applications.</p>
          
          <h2>What We Offer</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Blockchain APIs:</strong> Simple, powerful APIs for blockchain interactions</li>
            <li><strong>Marketplace Solutions:</strong> Ready-to-use blockchain solutions for various industries</li>
            <li><strong>Developer Tools:</strong> Comprehensive documentation and support for developers</li>
            <li><strong>Token Ecosystem:</strong> $BWS token for platform utility and developer grants</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Our Vision</h2>
          <p>We envision a future where blockchain technology seamlessly integrates into everyday business operations, enabling innovation, transparency, and trust across all industries.</p>
